;3月15日
3月15日，该国许多城市同时发生了许多抗议活动，数千名抗议者聚集在[[哈塞克|哈塞克]]、[[德拉|德拉]]、[[代尔祖尔|代尔祖尔]]和[[哈马|哈马]]。依据一些持不同政见者的组织的报道说，发生了一些示威者同安全部队之间的冲突。在大马士革，一个200人的集會很快发展至1500人，自1980年代以来该城市就很少有过类似的抗议发生。在一个正式名为“2011年叙利亚革命”（Syrian Revolution 2011）的[[Facebook|Facebook]]主页上，展示了许多发生在[[开罗|开罗]]、[[尼科西亚|尼科西亚]]、[[赫尔辛基|赫尔辛基]]、[[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]和[[柏林|柏林]]等地举行的示威活动的图片，以表达对叙利亚反政府示威活动的支持<ref>{{Cite news |title=السوريون يكسرون جدار الخوف بالتظاهر في قلب دمشق |author=Youtube/Al Arabiya |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rRHRxUxRbxo |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=2011年3月15日 |archive-date=2011年6月29日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629055303/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rRHRxUxRbxo |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=ردّدوا هتافات تدعو لمحاربة الفساد وفتح باب الحريات |author=Al Arabiya |url=http://www.alarabiya.net/articles/2011/03/15/141661.html |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=2011年3月15日 |archive-date=2011年4月3日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110403001329/http://www.alarabiya.net/articles/2011/03/15/141661.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=الاف السوريين يثورون في قلب دمشق و المحافظات مطالبين بالحرية |author=sawtbeirut.com |url=http://www.sawtbeirut.com/news-in-arabic/world-now/16474-syria-revolution-2011-march-15.html |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=2011年3月16日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110319034725/http://www.sawtbeirut.com/news-in-arabic/world-now/16474-syria-revolution-2011-march-15.html |archive-date=2011-03-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=مظاهرة شباب الثورة في تركيا |author=Youtube/Al Jazeera |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7AbjW0Kuhl8 |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=2011年3月16日 |archive-date=2011年3月18日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110318055645/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7AbjW0Kuhl8 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[苏海尔·阿塔西|苏海尔·阿塔西]]成为了“叙利亚革命”行动的非正式发言人，她被大量阿拉伯国家和其他国际媒体所采访。有报道说在大马士革有六人被逮捕<ref>{{Cite news |title=آخر اخبار انتفاضة سورية من فضائية الجزيرة |author=Youtube/Al Jazeera |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sMNBN1PhjzY |date= |accessdate=2011-03-15 |archive-date=2011-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110518090335/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sMNBN1PhjzY&feature=related |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=تقرير قناه ال BBC للانتفاضه السوريه |author=Youtube/BBC |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iAUOqfRSEaM |date= |accessdate=2011-03-15 |archive-date=2011-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110322001632/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iAUOqfRSEaM |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=مظاهرة احتجاج في دمشق تطالب بالحريات |author=BBC |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/arabic/middleeast/2011/03/110315_syria_protest.shtml |date= |accessdate=2011年3月15日 |archive-date=2014年8月1日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801214134/http://www.bbc.co.uk/arabic/middleeast/2011/03/110315_syria_protest.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她盛赞“那些主动走在前面的示威者”，“因为这让人想起刚刚发生在突尼斯和埃及的革命运动”<ref name="ahram" />。据报道大约有3000名抗议者被逮捕以及少数人牺牲了，不过还没有正式的死亡数字<ref>{{Cite news |title=معلومات عن سقوط شهداء في تظاهرات الثلاثاء في سوريا |author=sawtbeirut.com |url=http://sawtbeirut.com/news-in-arabic/world-now/16483-2011-03-16-18-33-05.html |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=2011年3月16日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110516012947/http://sawtbeirut.com/news-in-arabic/world-now/16483-2011-03-16-18-33-05.html |archive-date=2011-05-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

;3月16日
3月16日，叙利亚政府武力驱散了聚集在内政部前面的约200名抗议民众。[[阿拉伯卫星电视台|阿拉伯卫星电视台]]报道说这些人由社会活动人士、法学家、作家、记者、年轻学者以及被关押者家屬组成<ref>{{Cite news |title=Syrian Security Forces Break Up Damascus Protest |author=voanews.com |url=http://www.voanews.com/english/news/middle-east/Syrian-Security-Forces-Break-Up-Damascus-Protest-118085199.html |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=2011年3月16日 |archive-date=2011年4月4日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110404205509/http://www.voanews.com/english/news/middle-east/Syrian-Security-Forces-Break-Up-Damascus-Protest-118085199.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Rare public protest quashed in Syria |author=Al Jazeera |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/2011316131236735771.html |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=2011年3月16日 |archive-date=2011年3月17日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110317095713/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/2011316131236735771.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Syrian security forces disperse Damascus demo |author=AFP |url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5hN_8F5MkEvOPFuMqr-9HStxVy3iw?docId=CNG.e314ba0dc0a9061349e6fe1072be714a.5f1 |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=2011年3月16日 |archive-date=2014年2月25日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140225075922/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5hN_8F5MkEvOPFuMqr-9HStxVy3iw?docId=CNG.e314ba0dc0a9061349e6fe1072be714a.5f1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一些安全部队的官员尽力挤入到各个地方示威人群里面，并大声喊他们各自对总统忠诚的口号<ref>{{Cite news |title=بلطجية بشار |author=Youtube |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s0NcdFYFR0Q |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=2011年3月16日 |archive-date=2011年3月18日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110318055836/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s0NcdFYFR0Q |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=بلطجية بشار يفرقونا ويهتفون باسمه |author=Facebook Video |url=http://www.facebook.com/video/video.php?v=110837738996912&oid=420796315726&comments |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=2011年3月16日 |archive-date=2016年2月2日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202052911/https://www.facebook.com/video/video.php?v=110837738996912&oid=420796315726&comments |dead-url=no }}</ref>。部队也逮捕了许多抗议者，半島電視台报道说是25人<ref>{{Cite news |title=مظاهرة أمام القنصلية السورية في اسطنبول |author=Youtube |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CyXg8Hm8Hjs |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=16 March 2011 |archive-date=2012-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120118103806/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CyXg8Hm8Hjs |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而阿拉伯卫星电视台报道是32人<ref>{{Cite news |title=أسماء الناشطين المعتقلين من قبل قوات الأمن السورية |author=Youtube/Al Arabiya |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OJCttMTen2w |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=2011年3月16日 |archive-date=2011年3月18日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110318055824/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OJCttMTen2w |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其中有社会活动家兼律师[[苏海尔·阿塔西|苏海尔·阿塔西]]，以及两天前刚被释放的活动家Kamal Cheikho<ref>{{Cite news |title=أهالي سجناء وناشطون حقوقيون شاركوا في التجمع |author=Al Arabiya |url=http://www.alarabiya.net/articles/2011/03/16/141801.html |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=2011年3月16日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110403001021/http://www.alarabiya.net/articles/2011/03/16/141801.html |archive-date=2011年4月3日 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=اعتقالات وتفريق مظاهرة في دمشق |author=Al Jazeera |url=http://aljazeera.net/NR/exeres/04E7BD6C-CA0E-4597-A298-0494DD715056.html |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=16 March 2011 |archive-date=2011-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723011227/http://aljazeera.net/NR/exeres/04E7BD6C-CA0E-4597-A298-0494DD715056.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=سورية: مظاهرة امام وزارة الداخلية في العاصمة دمشق |author=BBC |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/arabic/middleeast/2011/03/110316_syria_prisoners_families.shtml |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=2011-03-16 |archive-date=2015-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150117224201/http://www.bbc.co.uk/arabic/middleeast/2011/03/110316_syria_prisoners_families.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[世界反酷刑组织|世界反酷刑组织]]（World Organisation Against Torture）发布了一份被逮捕人士的名单，并要求叙利亚政府立即释放他们<ref name="OMCT" />。

内政部的发言人Mohamed al-Ali则否认有示威活动的发生，并说“Facebook运动”被证明是不成功的。他还说“宣称的抗议”是由“躲藏在一堆发霉变质的人群里的人”组成，“他们只不过是想让人们看起来像是抗议罢了”<ref>{{Cite news |title=تصريح العميد العلي عن مظاهرة وزارة الداخلية |author=Youtube/Al Jazeera |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WevqUv1gGmw |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=2011-03-16 |archive-date=2011-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110318055810/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WevqUv1gGmw |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不过在另一个场合，他又承认了抗议的发生，但是他却说集会的人群是在表达支持总统的<ref>{{Cite news |title=وزارة الداخلية السورية – المظاهرات كانت لتأييد الرئيس |author=Youtube/BBC |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DXU4ascw1G0 |date= |accessdate=2011-03-15 |archive-date=2011-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110318055705/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DXU4ascw1G0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;3月18日
3月18日，叙利亚爆发了几十年来最严重的骚乱<ref name=aljaz18311>{{Cite news |title=Clashes erupt at protests in Syria |author=Aljazeera |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/201131817214964640.html |newspaper= |date= |accessdate=2011-03-18 |archive-date=2011-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110319115153/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/201131817214964640.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在“尊严星期五”（Friday of dignity）的号召行动下，周五的[[祷告|祷告]]活动后，数千人抗议者走上全国的大街要求结束政府腐败<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oC55uPBKYqU |title=Violence flares at Syrian protest |publisher=Youtube/Al Jazeera |date= |accessdate=2011-03-18 |archive-date=2012-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120918162029/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oC55uPBKYqU |dead-url=no }}</ref>。示威者受到安全部队的暴力镇压。示威者高呼“真主，叙利亚，自由”以及其他反腐败的口号<ref name=bbc18311>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-12791738|title=Middle East unrest: Two killed at protest in Syria|work=BBC News|date=2011-03-18|accessdate=2011-03-18|archive-date=2011-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110319063836/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-12791738|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

一些视频片段相继出现在YouTube和Twitter等网站，里面显示出许多城市的大量示威抗议活动，如[[大马士革|大马士革]]、[[德拉|德拉]]（Daraa）、[[霍姆斯|霍姆斯]]（Homs）、[[巴尼亚斯|巴尼亚斯]]（Baniyas）、[[卡米什利|卡米什利]]和[[代尔祖尔|代尔祖尔]]等城市<ref name="telegraph110318">{{Cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/8391438/Syria-four-dead-in-rare-demonstrations.html |title=Syria: 'four dead' in rare demonstrations |publisher=The Telegraph |date= |accessdate=2011-03-18 |archive-date=2018-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627223437/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/8391438/Syria-four-dead-in-rare-demonstrations.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ap110318">{{Cite news|url= http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5iFVmeKhYv0amn9vzUTAcH4HeEz4Q?docId=3b597c45357b466eae7fcd1d6f4d433d |title= 3 protesters killed in Syria, activist says |agency=Associated Press |date= |accessdate=2011-03-18}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url= http://www.ibtimes.com/articles/124507/20110318/syria.htm |title= Anti-government protests slowly erupting in Syria |publisher= IB Times |date=  |accessdate= 2011-03-18 |archive-date= 2011-03-21 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110321081237/http://www.ibtimes.com/articles/124507/20110318/syria.htm |dead-url= no }}</ref>。在大马士革，安全部队用暴力对付聚集在[[倭马亚大清真寺|倭马亚大清真寺]]前面的抗议民众，并拖走至少两位活动家<ref name=autogenerated3>{{Cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/8391438/Syria-four-dead-in-rare-demonstrations.html |title=Syria: 'four dead' in rare demonstrations |publisher=The Telegraph |date= |accessdate=2011-03-18 |archive-date=2018-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627223437/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/8391438/Syria-four-dead-in-rare-demonstrations.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在南部城市[[德拉|德拉]]，人们高喊反对总统的表弟[[拉米·马赫卢夫|拉米·马赫卢夫]]的口号。当局派出直升机和高壓水槍来驅散民众。有未经证实的报道说有四名抗议者被杀害，以及数百人受伤<ref name =aljaz18311/><ref name=bbc18311 />。一个居民说在德拉有三名抗议者被部队所杀<ref name=aljaz18311/>。叙利亚政府则宣称有未知的渗透者在该国制造了混乱<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://af.reuters.com/article/energyOilNews/idAFLDE72H1U520110318?sp=true |title=Syrian forces kill three protesters in southern city |publisher=Reuters |date= |accessdate=2011-03-18 |archive-date=2012-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120918134948/http://af.reuters.com/article/energyOilNews/idAFLDE72H1U520110318?sp=true |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

;3月19日
叙利亚军队发射催泪瓦斯以驱散在[[德拉|德拉]]聚集的人群，当时人们正在参加一场在前一天的反政府活动中被杀的两名抗议者的葬礼<ref name=bbc19311>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-12796020|title=Syria unrest: Tear gas fired at Deraa funeral|publisher=BBC News|date=2011-03-19|accessdate=2011-03-19|archive-date=2011-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110320014321/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-12796020|dead-url=no}}</ref>。人群高喊了“真主，叙利亚，自由”口号<ref name=bbc19311/>，目击者称当时军方使用的气体比普通的催泪瓦斯更具毒性<ref name=nyt19311>{{Cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/03/20/world/middleeast/20syria.html?_r=1&hp|title=Syrian Police Attack Mourners|work=The New York Times|date=2011-03-19|accessdate=2011-03-19|archive-date=2011-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110323112411/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/03/20/world/middleeast/20syria.html?_r=1&hp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。「敘利亞人權聯盟」表示有10名參與3月16日在内政部前面集会後被拘留的妇女開始絕食<ref name=afp19311>{{cite news|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5imPTFixkG47Y44ZniAQVv4wC6UGw?docId=CNG.301dc17b5d60dc6790da1726987ffe7d.c71|title=Syria funeral hit with teargas, protesters wounded: report|agency=AFP|date=2011-03-19|accessdate=2011-03-19|archive-date=2013-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013170559/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5imPTFixkG47Y44ZniAQVv4wC6UGw?docId=CNG.301dc17b5d60dc6790da1726987ffe7d.c71|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年3月19日，敘利亞总统下令将军队士兵服兵役的义务从21个月缩短到18个月<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-syria/syrian-mourners-call-for-revolt-forces-fire-tear-gas-idUSTRE72I22020110319 |title=Syrian mourners call for revolt, forces fire tear gas |publisher=Reuters |date=2011-03-19 |accessdate=2011-03-19 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924151947/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/03/19/us-syria-idUSTRE72I22020110319 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;3月20日
在德拉数千人连续第三天走上大街进行示威抗议，他们高喊反对国家紧急状态法的口号。军队朝他们开火，造成一人死亡几十人受伤<ref name="AJSyria20March">{{Cite news |title=Syria to free child prisoners |author=[[Al-Jazeera_English|Al-Jazeera English]] |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/2011320113138901721.html |newspaper= |date=2011-03-20 |accessdate=2011-03-20 |archive-date=2011-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110321113044/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/2011320113138901721.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。法院大樓、复兴党地方总部以及[[拉米·马赫卢夫|拉米·马赫卢夫]]的[[Syriatel|Syriatel]]建筑被示威者縱火<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/africa-mideast/syrian-protesters-set-fire-to-ruling-partys-headquarters-palace-of-justice/article1948865|title=Syrian protesters set fire to ruling party’s headquarters, Palace of Justice|work=The Globe and Mail|language=en|accessdate=2012-01-02|archive-date=2012-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120614083327/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/africa-mideast/syrian-protesters-set-fire-to-ruling-partys-headquarters-palace-of-justice/article1948865/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

3月20日，政府宣布释放15个孩子，他们是于3月6日由于以街頭塗鴉方式表達對民主的支持而被逮捕<ref name="AJSyria20March"/>。

=== 下旬 ===
;3月21日
抗议活动开始迅速地蔓延到整个国家<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://af.reuters.com/article/worldNews/idAFTRE72K6MP20110321?pageNumber=1&virtualBrandChannel=0 |title=Allies desert Yemeni leader, Syria protests spread |publisher=Reuters |date=21 March 2011 |accessdate=21 March 2011 |archive-date=2012-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120918135002/http://af.reuters.com/article/worldNews/idAFTRE72K6MP20110321?pageNumber=1&virtualBrandChannel=0 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在德拉数千人走上大街示威，部队也被派到了该地区<ref name=irtimes22311>{{Cite web |url=http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/world/2011/0322/1224292773018.html |title=US condemns Syria crackdown |publisher=Irish Times |date=22 March 2011 |accessdate=22 March 2011 |archive-date=2012-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023195348/http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/world/2011/0322/1224292773018.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在'''Jassem'''也有数百人举行着抗议，也有报道在[[巴尼亚斯|巴尼亚斯]]、[[霍姆斯|霍姆斯]]和[[哈马|哈马]]等地有不少抗议的发生<ref name=irtimes22311/><ref>{{Cite news|title=Protests spread to southern Syrian town Jassem|newspaper=Ya Libnan|date=2011-03-21|url=http://www.yalibnan.com/2011/03/21/protests-spread-to-southern-syrian-town-jassem/|accessdate=2011-03-21|archive-date=2011-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110322014938/http://www.yalibnan.com/2011/03/21/protests-spread-to-southern-syrian-town-jassem/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

有报道说，一名11岁的男孩在部队驱散德拉的人群中受伤，后来去世<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5ipLl3yeb_p-BMEyqG7WM2O9PYSbg?docId=CNG.e623321b6a9f7efb561fd470f40817bf.9d1|title=US condemns Syria crackdown|publisher=AFP|date=2011-03-21|accessdate=2011-03-21|archive-date=2011-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110325005057/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5ipLl3yeb_p-BMEyqG7WM2O9PYSbg?docId=CNG.e623321b6a9f7efb561fd470f40817bf.9d1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

德拉的抗议者在复兴党总部和其它政府建筑縱火。警察向人群發射實彈，目击者说导致至少一人死亡和数十人受伤。总统做了一些抚慰的表示，但是人们还是聚集在德拉的Omari清真寺，高喊他们的要求：释放所有政治犯；审判那些屠杀抗议者的人；废止实施了48年的紧急状态法；给予自由权；结束无处不在的腐败<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/03/21/world/middleeast/21syria.html |title=Officers Fire on Crowd as Syrian Protests Grow |publisher=NY Times |date=2011-03-20 |accessdate=2011-04-10 |archive-date=2011-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110324151608/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/03/21/world/middleeast/21syria.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;3月22日
在[[德拉|德拉]]、[[Jassem|Jassem]]、[[奈瓦|奈瓦]]和[[塞奈迈因|塞奈迈因]]都有抗议发生<ref name=aljaz22311>{{Cite web|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/2011322155925612161.html|title=UN calls for Syria probe as hundreds protest|publisher=Al Jazeera|date=2011-03-22|accessdate=2011-03-22|archive-date=2011-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110401071413/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/2011322155925612161.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=cnn22311>{{Cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/meast/03/22/syria.protests/?hpt=T2|title=Syria arrests opposition leader as protests continue|publisher=CNN|date=2011-03-22|accessdate=2011-03-22|archive-date=2011-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110515135003/http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/meast/03/22/syria.protests/?hpt=T2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。也有报道说在'''Inkhil'''和大马士革的农村地区发生了抗议<ref name=guardian22311>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/mar/22/syrian-protests-troops-kill-deraa |title=Syrian protests spread after troops kill at least five |work=The Guardian |location=UK |date=2011-03-22 |accessdate=2011-03-22 |archive-date=2011-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110322191124/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/mar/22/syrian-protests-troops-kill-deraa |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在德拉，聚集在Omari清真寺的大型抗议人群受到了一些枪击和催类瓦斯的对待<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-12827542 | title=Syria unrest: 'Gunfire heard' as Deraa protests go on | accessdate=2011-03-23 | date=2011-03-22 | publisher=BBC News Online | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5xO6FGBue?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-12827542 | archivedate=2011-03-23 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在德拉，一名[[法新社|法新社]]的摄影师和一个记者受到了部队的殴打，他们的器材也被夺走<ref name=aljaz22311/>。

联合国人权事务高专[[纳维·皮莱|纳维·皮莱]]呼吁调查3月份有六名抗议者被部队杀死的事件<ref name=aljaz22311/>。

此外当局又逮捕了著名的人权活动家Loay Hussein。<ref name=cnn22311/>

3月22日，《卫报》报道叙利亚政府组织了支持政府的示威运动，并且参与者还散布和宣传了一些是国内阴谋破坏者和外国渗透者制造了该国的动乱的言论<ref name=guardian22311/>。

;3月23日
据报道在该国南部至少有15名抗议者被部队所杀<ref name="cst23311">{{Cite web|url=http://www.suntimes.com/news/world/4472184-418/15-killed-in-clashes-in-southern-syria.html|title=15 killed in clashes in southern Syria|work=Chicago Sun=Times|date=23 March 2011|accessdate=23 March 2011|archive-date=2014-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140125104634/http://www.suntimes.com/news/world/4472184-418/15-killed-in-clashes-in-southern-syria.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。至少六人在德拉附近的'''Al-Omari清真寺'''被部队杀害，包括一名医生和一名护理人员<ref name="cst23311"/><ref name=bloom23311>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-23/four-people-killed-in-renewed-unrest-in-southern-syrian-town.html |title=Four People Killed in Renewed Unrest in Southern Syrian Town |publisher=Bloomberg |date=23 March 2011 |accessdate=23 March 2011 |archive-date=2011-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110414222315/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-23/four-people-killed-in-renewed-unrest-in-southern-syrian-town.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。目击者说有一名12岁的女孩在清真寺附近被部队杀害<ref name="cst23311"/>。

在白天，德拉地区的手机通讯服务被部队切断<ref name="cst23311"/>。部队也禁止救护车进入清真寺所在的市中心。

晚上，据报道部队朝向德拉行进的数百名年轻抗议者开枪<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-12843905|title=Syria unrest: Troops 'fire on youths in Deraa'|publisher=BBC News|date=2011-03-23|accessdate=2011-03-23|archive-date=2011-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110324031259/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-12843905|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

;3月24日
在德拉，大约20000人参加了被部队打死的九名抗议者的葬礼<ref>{{Cite news|title=Anger in Syria over crackdown|author=|publisher=Al Jazeera|date=24 Mar 2011|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/201132475046579830.html|accessdate=24 Mar 2011|archive-date=2011-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110324161252/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/201132475046579830.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该国人权委员会报告说死亡的抗议者升到了32人<ref>{{Cite news|title=Number of Syrian protestor deaths rises to 32, rights group reports|author=|agency=AFP  /NOW Lebanon|date=24 Mar 2011|url=http://nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=253703|accessdate=24 Mar 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110421122223/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=253703|archive-date=2011-04-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。法新社则报告说在德拉就有超过100人被部队所杀<ref>{{Cite news|title=More than 100 killed in Syria protest city|author=|agency=AFP  /NOW Lebanon|date=24 Mar 2011|url=http://nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=253836|accessdate=24 Mar 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110421122151/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=253836|archive-date=2011-04-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。该国自由作家Louai Hussein被拘留，因为在本周早些时候他曾公布了一份要求获取自由表达权利的请愿书<ref>{{Cite news|title=Syria frees writer detained for online activity|author=|agency=AFP  /NOW Lebanon|date=24 Mar 2011|url=http://nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=254083|accessdate=24 Mar 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110421121946/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=254083|archive-date=2011-04-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

3月24日，总统发言人布赛奈·沙班声明政府将会研究取消紧急状态法和允许其他政党成立的可行性。政府也宣布会削减个人所得税，公务员个人工资每月增加1500叙利亚圆（32.60美元），并保证扩大出版自由，创造更多的就业机会和降低腐败<ref>{{cite news |title=Syria pledges reforms after protests |author= |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/2011324164740741279.html |date=2011-03-24 |accessdate=2011-03-24 |archive-date=2011-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110325121701/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/2011324164740741279.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Syria unrest: Government pledges political reforms |author=BBC |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-12853634 |newspaper= |date=2011-03-24 |accessdate=2011-03-24 |archive-date=2011-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110325220742/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-12853634 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;3月25日
[[File:SyrianAngerRevolution.jpg|thumb]]
在一个计划于周五祷告后举行一场以“愤怒星期五”为口号的大型抗议活动的呼吁下，上万人涌上全国的大街，以反抗政府对示威者使用致命的暴力措施。在该国的南部军队朝示威者开枪，杀死了一些和平示威者，根据目击者陈述和新闻报道，这个严重的伤害事件使国家进入了混乱<ref>{{Cite news|title=Syrian Troops Open Fire on Protesters in Several Cities|agency=Reuters|date=25 Mar 2011|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/03/26/world/middleeast/26syria.html?ref=syria|accessdate=2011-04-10|archive-date=2013-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131010012526/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/03/26/world/middleeast/26syria.html?ref=syria|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

有报道，在德拉10万人举行的抗议中至少20人被杀害<ref name=cnn25311>{{Cite news|title=In Syrian flashpoint town, more deaths reported|publisher=CNN|date=25 March 2011|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/meast/03/25/syria.unrest/index.html?hpt=T1|accessdate=25 Mar 2011|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304033600/http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/meast/03/25/syria.unrest/index.html?hpt=T1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Security Forces 'Kill 20 Protesters' In Syria |publisher=Sky News|date=25 March 2011|url=http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/World-News/Video-Syria-Security-Forces-Open-Fire-On-Protesters-Killing-20-People-According-To-Reports/Article/201103415960221?lpos=World_News_Top_Stories_Header_3&lid=ARTICLE_15960221_Video%2C_Syria%3A_Security_Fzorces_Open_Fire_On_Protesters_Killing_20_People%2C_According_To_Reports|accessdate=2011-03-25}}</ref>。一个目击者说数千人高喊反对总统兄弟的口号: “[[马希尔·阿萨德|马希尔·阿萨德]]你这个懦夫，有本事派你的军队去解放[[戈蘭高地|戈蘭]]”<ref>{{Cite news|title=Syrian protesters denounce Assad's brother|agency=Reuters|date=2011-03-25|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/03/25/syria-protest-assad-idUSLDE72O17Y20110325|accessdate=2011-03-25|archive-date=2013-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224121354/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/03/25/syria-protest-assad-idUSLDE72O17Y20110325|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。一座[[哈菲兹·阿萨德|哈菲兹·阿萨德]]的雕像被拆除且被火烧了<ref name=AlJazeera260311>{{Cite news|title=Syrian protesters target Baath Party offices|publisher=Al Jazeera|date=26 Mar 2011|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/201132616546326475.html|accessdate=26 Mar 2011|archive-date=2011-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110405193002/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/201132616546326475.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。政府驻地也有人放火<ref name=AlJazeera260311/>。

在大马士革、[[代爾祖爾|代爾祖爾]]、[[霍姆斯|霍姆斯]]、[[拉塔基亚|拉塔基亚]]（Latakia）和[[拉卡|拉卡]]（Ar-Raqqah）也有抗议发生<ref name=cnn25311/><ref name=Haaretz250311>{{Cite news|title=At least 23 said killed as protesters in Syria clash with security forces|newspaper=Haaretz|date=25 March 2011|url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/international/at-least-23-said-killed-as-protesters-in-syria-clash-with-security-forces-1.351815|accessdate=26 March 2011|archive-date=2011-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110327091432/http://www.haaretz.com/news/international/at-least-23-said-killed-as-protesters-in-syria-clash-with-security-forces-1.351815|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在拉塔基亚和霍姆斯分别有一名抗议者被部队打死<ref>{{Cite news|title=SYRIA: Government forces open fire on protesters|work=Los Angeles Times|date=24 March 2011|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/babylonbeyond/2011/03/syria-government-forces-open-fire-on-protesters.html|accessdate=24 Mar 2011|archive-date=2011-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928030710/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/babylonbeyond/2011/03/syria-government-forces-open-fire-on-protesters.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。也有报道说在全国有许多人被打死<ref>{{Cite news|title=SYRIA: Government forces open fire on protesters|work=LA Times|date=25 March 2011|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/babylonbeyond/2011/03/syria-government-forces-open-fire-on-protesters.html|accessdate=25 Mar 2011|archive-date=2011-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928030710/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/babylonbeyond/2011/03/syria-government-forces-open-fire-on-protesters.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在[[塞奈迈因|塞奈迈因]]，有目击者说20人被部队打死<ref name=Haaretz250311/><ref>{{Cite news|title=Deaths as Syrian forces fire on protesters|publisher=AL Jazeera|date=26 Mar 2011|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/2011325145817688433.html|accessdate=26 Mar 2011|archive-date=2011-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110903223754/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/2011325145817688433.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。叙利亚官方新闻机构却说“一些罪犯”袭击了军队首领，因此“导致几个袭击者死亡”<ref name=SANA250311>{{Cite news|title=Armed Gang Attacks People's Army Headquarter, Several Attackers killed... Another Armed Gang Attacks Officers Club in Homs and Opens Fire, Martyring a Citizen|author=M.Nassr/Ghossoun/H. Sabbagh|newspaper=Syrian Arab News Agency|date=25 March 2011|url=http://www.sana.sy/eng/21/2011/03/25/338516.htm|accessdate=26 March 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111004164838/http://www.sana.sy/eng/21/2011/03/25/338516.htm|archive-date=2011-10-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

在德拉，有许多人因在一起团结着高喊要求自由和反对政治腐败的口号而被打死<ref name="violence-syria">{{Cite news|title=Violence erupts in Syria; troops open fire on anti-protestors|publisher=New York Daily Times|date=2011-03-25|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/world/2011/03/25/2011-03-25_violence_erupts_in_syria_troops_open_fire_on_antiprotestors_.html?r=news|accessdate=2011-03-25|archive-date=2020-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200308184439/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/world/2011/03/25/2011-03-25_violence_erupts_in_syria_troops_open_fire_on_antiprotestors_.html?r=news|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在'''Tafas'''，三名抗议者被部队打死<ref name=AlJazeera260311/>。在'''Kafr Amim'''，有人在复兴党总部放了火<ref name="110325AFP">{{Cite news|title=25 March 2011 Syrian Protests|publisher=AFP/NOW Lebanon|date=25 March 2011|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=254495|accessdate=25 Mar 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110419043652/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=254495|archive-date=2011-04-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

[[逊尼派|逊尼派]]教士首领Yusuf al-Qaradawi，在[[卡塔尔|卡塔尔]]布道说“今天，革命的火车已经抵达了应该到达的站点—叙利亚站。叙利亚不可能与阿拉伯世界的历史相分离<ref name=wsj25311>{{cite news |url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748704517404576222350109783770.html |title=Troops Open Fire on Syrian Protesters |work=The Wall Street Journal |date=25 March 2011 |accessdate=25 March 2011 |first=Farnaz |last=Fassihi |archive-date=2011-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110925145448/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748704517404576222350109783770.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。叙利亚的[[什叶派|什叶派]]教士首领Adnan al-Arour，建议抗议的年轻人应该向埃及革命学习，不要采取暴力行为。他希望总统能设立一个对话委员会以聆听示威者合法的委屈心声<ref>{{Cite news|title=الشيخ عدنان العرعور يساند الثورة السورية و درعا|publisher=Youtube|date=25 March 2011|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bo3odWm5f-s|accessdate=25 Mar 2011|archive-date=2011-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110423123521/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bo3odWm5f-s|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

法新社报道说，流亡的叙利亚反对派领袖要求法国把总统阿萨德赶下台，呼吁法国对叙利亚政府采取措施以防止继续滥杀无辜<ref name="110325AFP" />。有YouTube视频显示，在[[阿勒颇|阿勒颇]]的大清真寺里抗议者们受到袭击和殴打<ref>{{Cite news|title=الاعتداءعلى مظاهرات حلب الجامع الكبير 25 أذار|publisher=Youtube|date=2011-03-25|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=kj0pOlSV3GM|accessdate=2011-03-25|archive-date=2015-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151218221034/https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=kj0pOlSV3GM|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另一个视频显示，一些抗议者涌进大马士革的'''Ar-Rifai清真寺'''，他们高喊 “真主，叙利亚，自由”口号<ref>{{Cite news|title=الثورة السورية جمعة العزة جامع الرفاعي 25 آذار|publisher=Youtube|date=2011-03-25|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PcVmPGQsoIM|accessdate=2011-03-25|archive-date=2011-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110329013951/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PcVmPGQsoIM|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一个相关的YouTube视频像一部电影一样，是在[[霍姆斯|霍姆斯]]拍摄的，内容是安全部队改穿上平民服装，目的是想激怒那些抗议者<ref>{{Cite news|title=حمص المندسين|publisher=Youtube|date=2011-03-25|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=mV301r7rOPo|accessdate=2011-03-25|archive-date=2011-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110611165443/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mV301r7rOPo&feature=player_embedded|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在通往德拉的路上，有17名示威者被杀；有40人在'''Omari清真寺'''附近死去；25人死于[[霍姆斯|霍姆斯]]的'''al-Sanameen'''地区；4人死于[[拉塔基亚|拉塔基亚]]；3人死于大马士革<ref name="110325AFP" />。

;3月26日
敘利亞政府释放超过200名政治犯，其中大约70人是大部分被关押在Saidnaya监狱里的[[伊斯兰主义|伊斯兰主义]]者。<ref name="BBCSyria26Mar">{{cite news |title=Syria turmoil: Political inmates 'freed' after protests |author=BBC |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-12870679 |newspaper= |date=2011-03-26 |accessdate=2011-03-26 |archive-date=2011-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110405203559/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-12870679 |dead-url=no }}</ref>日落时分，至少有两个城市的复兴党办公地起火。部署在[[拉塔基亚|拉塔基亚]]军队朝周围的人群开火<ref name="NYTIMES">{{Cite web |url=http://topics.nytimes.com/top/news/international/countriesandterritories/syria/index.html |title=NY Times:Syria – Protests (2011) |publisher=NY Times |date= |accessdate=2011-04-10 |archive-date=2011-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511141803/http://topics.nytimes.com/top/news/international/countriesandterritories/syria/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在[[拉塔基亚|拉塔基亚]]和'''Tafas'''的复兴党所在地和警察局都设置了军力<ref name=AlJazeera260311/>。政府谴责“武装的暴徒在试图破坏国家的稳定”。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/mobile/world-middle-east-12873053 |title=BBC news:Syria unrest |publisher=BBC News |date= |accessdate=2011-04-10 |archive-date=2011-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110405203549/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/mobile/world-middle-east-12873053 |dead-url=no }}</ref>政府控制的叙利亚新闻机构（SANA），宣称一个占领了拉塔基亚的许多地方的武装团伙，朝公民和部队人员开火<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dp-news.com/pages/detail.aspx?l=2&articleId=79055|title=Damascus was Quite on Saturday|publisher=DP-news}}{{Dead link|date=2020年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。在德拉，数千人抗议中有两人被杀<ref name=AlJazeera260311/>。两个美国公民被以参与了抗议活动的名义而被叙利亚政府拘留，两人分别为32岁的拥有埃及和美国双重国籍的Mohammed Radwan，和来自[[佛蒙特州|佛蒙特州]]21岁的Middlebury学院的学生Pathik Tik Root<ref>{{Cite news|title=Syrians detain 2 Americans during demonstrations|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2011/03/26/syrians-detain-2-americans-demonstrations/#ixzz1Hq4qnEiT|accessdate=2011-03-27|publisher=Fox News|date=2011-03-26|agency=Associated Press|location=Cairo|quote=Syrian authorities have detained two Americans amid an unprecedented wave of protests in the repressive Middle East nation, relatives and state media said Saturday.|archive-date=2011-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110401201248/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2011/03/26/syrians-detain-2-americans-demonstrations/#ixzz1Hq4qnEiT|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[霍姆斯|霍姆斯]]的地方领导人因该地发生的死亡事件被解职了。叙利亚驻[[印度|印度]]大使为抗议本国发生的屠杀也辞职了<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=254752|title=Syria 26 March 2011|publisher=AFP/NOW Lebanon|access-date=2012-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120103080348/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=254752|archive-date=2012-01-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

;3月27日
叙利亚官方说有12人在[[拉塔基亚|拉塔基亚]]死亡<ref>{{Cite news|title=US will not intervene in Syria as it has in Libya, says Hillary Clinton|author=Staff and agencies|newspaper=guardian.co.uk|date=2011-03-27|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/mar/27/report-12-killed-syrian-port-city|accessdate=2011-03-27|archive-date=2011-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110413051634/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/mar/27/report-12-killed-syrian-port-city|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一个由半島電視台上传到的YouTube的片段显示，'''Ar-Rahman清真寺'''的[[伊玛目|伊玛目]]（清真寺内率领伊斯兰教徒做礼拜的人）告诉他们说该城市正在发生大屠杀<ref>{{Cite news|title=إتصال لإمام مسجد الرحمن باللاذقية|publisher=Al Jazeera/Youtube|date=2011-03-27|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sdqNRXiyI84|accessdate=2011-03-27|archive-date=2011-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110401030522/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sdqNRXiyI84|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

总统顧問Buthaina Shaaban说紧急状态法将会废除，但是没有谈具体时间。她也说总统会公开露面讲话，以表达政府的态度和下一步采取的行动<ref name=AlJazeeraEnglish270311>{{Cite news|title=Syria 'to lift emergency law'|author=Al-Jazeera English|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/201132711553545999.html|date=2011-03-27|accessdate=2011-03-27|archive-date=2011-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110329101837/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/201132711553545999.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[路透社|路透社]]报道说，他们的两名记者失踪了，最后一次联系是在前晚，当时二人正准备从叙利亚进入黎巴嫩。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Two Reuters TV journalists missing in Syria|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/03/27/us-syria-reuters-idUSTRE72Q27E20110327|accessdate=27 March 2011|agency=Reuters|date=27 March 2011|location=London|quote=Two Reuters television journalists have been missing in Syria since Saturday night, when they were due to return to Lebanon.|archive-date=2011-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110328111333/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/03/27/us-syria-reuters-idUSTRE72Q27E20110327|dead-url=yes}}</ref>'''Al Arabiya'''报道说，叙利亚将修改宪法第八章里有关对复兴党所做的限制性的内容<ref>{{Cite news|title=Syria to change Article 8 in the constitution that limits rule to the Baath Party|newspaper=AlArabiya English|date=27 March 2011|url=http://twitter.com/AlArabiya_Eng/status/52018520573227008|accessdate=27 March 2011|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220032320/https://twitter.com/AlArabiya_Eng/status/52018520573227008|dead-url=no}}</ref>。记者Sobhi Hasan和Zaher Alamin又被逮捕了<ref>{{Cite news|title=Syria rearrests journalists Sobhi Hasan and Zaher Alamin|newspaper=AlArabiya English|date=27 March 2011|url=http://twitter.com/AlArabiya_Eng/status/52005340757229568#|accessdate=27 March 2011|archive-date=2016-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202052911/https://twitter.com/AlArabiya_Eng/status/52005340757229568|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

;3月28日
在德拉，一个目击者说，部队用武力强行驱散了数百名要求结束紧急状态法的示威人群，不过即使面对重型武器的威胁，人群还是又重新聚集了<ref name="NYTIMES"/>。

[[路透社|路透社]]报道说失踪的两名记者都是黎巴嫩国籍的，他们是从3月26日被叙利亚当局拘留，在獲释后已返回黎巴嫩<ref name=autogenerated2>{{Cite news|title=Reuters: Journalists detained in Syria freed|url=http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/nationworld/2014620010_apsyriamissingjournalists.html|accessdate=28 March 2011|newspaper=[[The_Seattle_Times|The Seattle Times]]|date=28 March 2011|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|location=London|quote=International news agency Reuters says two of its journalists detained by Syrian authorities have been released. Reuters said Monday its television producer Ayat Basma and cameraman Ezzat Baltaji, both Lebanese nationals, have returned to Lebanon. It says they were detained by Syrian authorities on Saturday.|archive-date=2011-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110329045644/http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/nationworld/2014620010_apsyriamissingjournalists.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

有证人说，国会议员Youssef Abu Roumieh和Ahmad al-Moqdad，以及复兴党书记处的委员Abed al-Latif al-Moqdad，因抗议在德拉-{}-发生的屠杀而辞职<ref>{{Cite news |title=Syria: 28 March 2011 |url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=255457 |accessdate=2011-03-28 |agency=AFP |website=NOW Lebanon |date=2011-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110402133709/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=255457 |archive-date=2011-04-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

科威特的[[谢赫_(称号)|谢赫]]（宗教领袖）Nabeel al-Awadi<ref>{{Cite news|title=الشيخ نبيل العوضي يتحدث عن ثورة سوريا ويساندها|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=gC2u_W1j4hY|accessdate=2011-03-28|publisher=Youtube|date=2011-03-28|archive-date=2015-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109113805/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gC2u_W1j4hY&feature=player_embedded|dead-url=no}}</ref>和叙利亚的谢赫Issam al-Attar<ref>{{Cite news|title=شام – الشيخ عصام العطار الى أهالي درعا|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YIY_52aaU6w&feature=player_embedded|accessdate=2011-03-28|publisher=Youtube|date=2011-03-28|archive-date=2016-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202052911/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YIY_52aaU6w&feature=player_embedded|dead-url=no}}</ref>都表示他们支持反政府示威。

;3月29日
在[[大马士革|大马士革]]、[[阿勒颇|阿勒颇]]、[[霍姆斯|霍姆斯]]、[[哈塞克|哈塞克]]、[[塔尔图斯|塔尔图斯]]和[[哈马|哈马]]几个城市有数万人举行表达支持总统的集会<ref>{{Cite news|title=Syria unrest: Pro-Assad rallies in Damascus and Aleppo|publisher=BBC News|date=29 March 2011|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-12892870|accessdate=29 March 2011|archive-date=2011-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110405203552/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-12892870|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dp-news.com/pages/detail.aspx?l=2&articleId=79305 |title=Mass Popular Rallies Prevail Syrian Provinces in Support of National Unity, Security and Stability |publisher=DP-News |date=2011-03-29 |accessdate=2011-04-10 }}{{Dead link|date=2020年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name=Ynetnews290311>{{Cite news|title=Assad supporters 'loyal to nation'|author=|newspaperYnetnews=|date=29 March 2011|url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4049313,00.html|accessdate=29 March 2011|archive-date=2011-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110513141859/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0%2C7340%2CL-4049313%2C00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同日内阁向总统提出正式請辞<ref name=AJSyriaGovQuit>{{cite web |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/201132975114399138.html |title=Syrian cabinet resigns amid unrest |work=Al Jazeera |date=2011-03-29 |accessdate=2011-04-15 |archive-date=2011-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110415090333/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/201132975114399138.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

该国男演员Jamal Suliman通过BBC代表该国的艺术家们发表了一项针对目前举行的示威活动的声明：他们认识到了“执行改革”的重要性，并且愿意与“处于迫切性和改革进程的政治体系”站在一起，“正如他们与人民站在一起一样”<ref>{{Cite news|title=بيان الفنانين السوريين|author=|BBC/Youtube=|date=29 March 2011|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=E7cHGl8vZWs|accessdate=29 March 2011|archive-date=2016-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202052911/https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=E7cHGl8vZWs|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

;3月30日
总统发表了一个讲话，他指责“外国阴谋”导致了示威活动的产生，并且宣布紧急状态法不会如Bouthaina Shaaban之前宣布的一样会被废除，相反还会研究该法未来的用途<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/2011330135615434966.html |title=Syria's Assad warns of 'conspiracy' – Middle East – Al Jazeera English |publisher=English.aljazeera.net |date=2011-03-31 |accessdate=2011-04-10 |archive-date=2011-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110405192025/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/2011330135615434966.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

一些不滿意阿萨德讲话的抗议者在[[拉塔基亚|拉塔基亚]]涌上了大街，被警察开火攻击<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/03/30/syria-protest-latakia-idUSLDE72T1ZQ20110330 |title=Protests in Latakia after Assad speech -residents |publisher=Reuters |date= |accessdate=2011-04-10 |archive-date=2011-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110330172731/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/03/30/syria-protest-latakia-idUSLDE72T1ZQ20110330 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://en.trend.az/regions/met/arabicr/1853160.html |title=Syrian police fire at protesters in Latakia | Arabic region | Trend |publisher=En.trend.az |date=2011-03-30 |accessdate=2011-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511020408/http://en.trend.az/regions/met/arabicr/1853160.html |archive-date=2011-05-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在[[德拉|德拉]]，许多不满总统讲话的抗议者举行了示威，有五人死亡，从而使该地区喪生的抗议者累积至200人。大马士革的调查法官拒绝释放[[苏海尔·阿塔西|苏海尔·阿塔西]]和其他四名社会活动家<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=256241 |title=Syria: 30 March 2011 |publisher=AFP/NOW Lebanon |date=2011-03-30 |accessdate=2011-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110419043646/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=256241 |archive-date=2011-04-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

;3月31日
又有两名路透社记者Suleiman al-Khalidi和Khaled al-Hariri在叙利亚失踪<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=256300 |title=Two more Reuters journalists disappear in Syria |publisher=NOW Lebanon |date=2011-03-31 |accessdate=2011-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110419173841/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=256300 |archive-date=2011-04-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

敘利亞总统设立一个由专家组成的委员会，研究为废止紧急状态法所要解决的法律问题；同时又成立一个司法委员会，调查导致公民和安全部队在德拉和拉塔基亞喪生的一些事件。<ref>{{cite news |title=Assad orders review of Syrian laws |author= |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/201133113439956857.html |newspaper= |date=2011-03-31 |accessdate=2011-04-01 |archive-date=2011-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110401060715/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/201133113439956857.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

总统巴沙尔·阿萨德颁佈法令，于4月1日增加政府雇员的工资<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=256392|title=Assad issues decree to raise wages|publisher=NOW Lebanon|date=2011-03-31|accessdate=2011-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110419113204/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=256392|archive-date=2011-04-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

一个位于伦敦的民权组织告诉[[穆斯林兄弟会|穆斯林兄弟会]]说，在周四叙利亚西北部的[[拉塔基亚|拉塔基亚]]有25人在“大屠杀中”（bloodbath）被部队所杀<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=256458|title=Several killed in Latakia "bloodbath," NGO says|publisher=NOW Lebanon|date=2011-03-31|accessdate=2011-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110420234426/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=256458|archive-date=2011-04-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 四月 ==

=== 上旬 ===
;4月1日-“'''烈士星期五'''”
在一个口号为“烈士星期五”（Friday of martyrs）呼吁下，超过25万名示威者在祷告之后，走上全国许多城市的大街举行抗议。在大马士革的郊区'''Douma'''，部队朝大约1000人的抗议人群开枪，杀死了8人。在市区，几百名抗议者聚集在'''Al Rifai'''清真寺，有报道说部队密封了该寺并攻击想要离开那里的抗议群众。在南部[[德拉|德拉]]，一名抗议者被杀<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4050879,00.html |title=At least 10 killed in Syria |publisher=Ynetnews.com |date= |accessdate=2011-04-10 |archive-date=2016-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807191825/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4050879,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Syrian Protesters Clash With Security Forces|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/04/02/world/middleeast/02syria.html?ref=world|accessdate=2011-04-01|newspaper=NYTimes|date=2011-04-01|author=LIAM STACK|author2=J. DAVID GOODMAN|archive-date=2011-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110405184022/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/04/02/world/middleeast/02syria.html?ref=world|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

叙利亚政府关闭了它与[[土耳其|土耳其]]之间的边境，以阻止土耳其人和外国记者进入该国<ref name="NL110401">{{Cite news|title=Syria: 1 April 2011|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=256994|accessdate=1 April 2011|agency=AFP  /NOW Lebanon|date=1 April 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120103080331/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=256994|archive-date=2012-01-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在德拉，部队不让下午在'''Omari'''清真寺里的人离开去参加游行<ref>{{Cite news|title=BBC Arabic reports protests in multiple Syrian cities|url=http://nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=256829#ixzz1IHJUCiZz|accessdate=2011-04-01|agency=AFP  /NOW Lebanon|date=2011-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110420234328/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=256829#ixzz1IHJUCiZz|archive-date=2011-04-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。一名路透社通讯员在被拘留三天后獲释<ref>{{Cite news|title=Reuters journalist freed in Syria, photographer missing|url=http://nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=256951#ixzz1II9nqnJb|accessdate=1 April 2011|agency=AFP  /NOW Lebanon|date=2011-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110429150031/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=256951#ixzz1II9nqnJb|archive-date=2011-04-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

有10人在南部的'''Enkhel'''和'''Sanamen'''之间的军事检查站被杀。在大马士革北部的'''Douma'''，部队朝示威者开火，导致至少4人死亡和几十人受伤<ref name="NL110401"/>。

;4月2日
一个人权组织表示，数千名[[德魯茲人|德魯茲人]]在[[戈兰高地|戈兰高地]]的'''Buq'ata'''举行了支持总统的示威<ref>{{Cite news|title=Golan Heights: Thousands of Druze protest in solidarity with Assad|newspaper=Ynetnews|date=2 April 2011|url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4050968,00.html|accessdate=2 April 2011|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002050735/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4050968,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在[[德拉|德拉]]和[[霍姆斯|霍姆斯]]安全部队逮捕了超过20人<ref>{{Cite news |title=Many arrested in Syria after protests |author= |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/20114211257594538.html |newspaper= |date=2 April 2011 |accessdate=2 April 2011 |archive-date=2011-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110405193025/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/20114211257594538.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

土耳其总理[[埃爾多安|埃爾多安]]说他会敦促阿萨德进行改革<ref>{{Cite web |last=Brown |first=Cameron S. |url=http://www.jpost.com/MiddleEast/Article.aspx?id=214849 |title=Erdogan says he will press Syria's Assad to reform |work=Jerusalem Post |location=Israel |date= |accessdate=2011-04-10 |archive-date=2011-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511180246/http://www.jpost.com/MiddleEast/Article.aspx?id=214849 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;4月3日
叙利亚当局释放被拘留六天的50岁[[路透社|路透社]]摄影师Khaled al-Hariri<ref>{{Cite news|title=Syria frees Reuters photographer after six days|url=http://www.jpost.com/Headlines/Article.aspx?id=214978|accessdate=2011-04-03|newspaper=[[Jerusalem_Post|Jerusalem Post]]|date=2011-04-03|agency=Reuters|location=London|quote=Syrian authorities freed Reuters photographer Khaled al-Hariri on Sunday, six days after detaining him as he arrived for work in Damascus last Monday. Hariri, 50, who has worked for Reuters for over 20 years in his native Syria, met colleagues in the capital after his release and told them he was well.|archive-date=2012-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023203134/http://www.jpost.com/Headlines/Article.aspx?id=214978|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

阿萨德指定[[阿德爾·薩法爾|阿德爾·薩法爾]]为新总理人选，并让他负责组建新政府<ref>{{Cite news|title=Bashar Assad appoints Adel Safar new PM of Syria|url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/deaths-arrests-in-syrian-clashes/story-e6frg6so-1226032915783|accessdate=2011-04-03|newspaper=The Australian|date=2011-04-04|agency=[[Agence_France-Presse|AFP]], [[Associated_Press|AP]]|quote=SYRIAN President Bashar Assad last night asked former agriculture minister Adel Safar to form a new government, as communications networks failed and residents in Douma prepared to bury the first of their dead.|archive-date=2011-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110822210749/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/deaths-arrests-in-syrian-clashes/story-e6frg6so-1226032915783|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[法新社|法新社]]报道周日不能进行网络通讯，手机也没有信号，虽然地面的线路看起来是正常的<ref>{{Cite news|title=Syrian cell phones, internet down after wave of arrests|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=257364|accessdate=3 April 2011|agency=AFP  /NOW Lebanon|date=3 April 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110419113138/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=257364|archive-date=2011-04-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

;4月4日

阿萨德指定Mohammad Khaled al-Hannus任德拉的地方领导人<ref>{{Cite news |title=Assad appoints new governor for Daraa |author= |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/201144134848651549.html |newspaper= |date=2011-04-05 |accessdate=2011-04-05 |archive-date=2011-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110405035606/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/201144134848651549.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同时，在大马士革外面的'''Douma'''地区，数千人走上大街游行并高喊反政府的口号<ref name="NYTIMES" />。

叙利亚国家新闻机构（SANA）报道，在[[拉塔基亚|拉塔基亚]]的一个监狱里，有一名囚犯放火，导致8名囚犯死亡和两名警察被烧伤<ref>{{Cite news|title=إضرام النار من قبل أحد المساجين في جناح بسجن اللاذقية المركزي يودي بحياة ثمانية مساجين|url=http://www.sana.sy/ara/163/2011/04/04/339973.htm|accessdate=2011-04-04|newspaper=Syrian Arab News Agency|date=2011-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110407082951/http://www.sana.sy/ara/163/2011/04/04/339973.htm|archive-date=2011-04-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

;4月5日
法新社报道，为了纪念那些过去一段时间大量抗议者的被杀，革命发起方组织的一系列以“烈士周”为主题的（Martyrs Week）集会开始了<ref>{{Cite news|title=Syria braces for "Martyrs Week" of protests|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=258075|accessdate=5 April 2011|newspaper=NOW Lebanon|date=5 April 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110419113058/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=258075|archive-date=2011-04-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在大马士革附近，两名警察被身份不明的枪手射杀<ref>{{Cite news|title=Two Syrian police killed by gunmen – state TV|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/05/syria-police-idUSLDE7341YC20110405|accessdate=2011-04-05|agency=Reuters|date=2011-04-05|location=[[Beirut|Beirut]]|quote=|archive-date=2011-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110728130451/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/05/syria-police-idUSLDE7341YC20110405|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在'''Kafr Batna'''有15名示威者被杀<ref>{{Cite news|title=Syria: 5 April 2011|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=258403|accessdate=2011-04-05|agency=AFP|website=NOW Lebanon|date=2011-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110409205641/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=258403|archive-date=2011-04-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

;4月6日
阿萨德政府做了一些对逊尼派和库尔德人善意的表示：宣布于2010年新年除夕开张的让[[伊斯兰主义|伊斯兰主义]]者愤恨的赌场将会关闭；也说由于穿[[尼卡布|尼卡布]]而被开除的教师可以重返学校工作；<ref name="NYTIMES"/>上万名居住在叙利亚的库尔德人也会获得叙利亚公民权。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Many Kurds will be granted Syrian citizenship, As-Safir reports|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=258435|accessdate=2011-04-06|agency=AFP|website=NOW Lebanon|date=2011-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110419113051/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=258435|archive-date=2011-04-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

政府报纸'''Teshreen'''的编辑说，她正在组织与关键的一些反对派人士的对话，目的是听取他们对政治改革的要求<ref>{{Cite news|title=Syrian regime prepares talks with opponents|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=258402|accessdate=6 April 2011|agency=AFP  /NOW Lebanon|date=6 April 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110419113055/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=258402|archive-date=2011-04-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。一位亲政府的政治人物表示，叙利亚议会正准备于5月进行一次大的改革，包括结束紧急状态法<ref>{{Cite news|title=Syrian lawmakers pave the way to end emergency rule|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=258617|accessdate=6 April 2011|agency=AFP  /NOW Lebanon|date=6 April 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110419113041/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=258617|archive-date=2011-04-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

;4月7日
叙利亚的法学家们完成了一个新法规的草案，内容是代替紧急状态法和属于复兴党成员的宗教领袖的税法<ref name="NL110407">{{Cite web|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=259218|title=Syria: 7 April 2011|publisher=AFP/NOW Lebanon|date=2011-04-07|accessdate=2011-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110410114321/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=259218|archive-date=2011-04-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。国际人权组织呼吁联合国人权委员会对目前叙利亚国内存在的人权危机进行干预，最好尽快能举办一个特别会议<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=258939|title=Human Rights NGOs call UN to convene on Syria|publisher=NOW Lebanon|date=2011-04-07|accessdate=2011-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110419113020/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=258939|archive-date=2011-04-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

4月7日，敘利亞总统解散[[霍姆斯省|霍姆斯省]]政府，並颁布法令向数千名居住在[[哈塞克省|哈塞克省]]的库尔德人給予叙利亚国籍<ref>{{cite news |title=Assad attempts to appease minority Kurds |author= |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/20114711251531744.html |date=2011-04-07 |accessdate=2011-04-07 |archive-date=2011-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111006185522/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/20114711251531744.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。叙利亚的一些人权观察组织说48名库尔德人被释放<ref>{{cite news |title=Syria frees 48 Kurds, hoping to ease grievances |author= |url=http://af.reuters.com/article/worldNews/idAFTRE7361P720110407 |date=2011-04-07 |accessdate=2011-04-07 |archive-date=2016-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817131430/http://af.reuters.com/article/worldNews/idAFTRE7361P720110407 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。随后总统与库尔德部落的领袖举行了会面，谈论了居住在叙利亚东北部的库尔德人的公民身份权问题，这些库尔德人在1962年国家人口统计后丧失了公民权<ref>{{cite news |title=Syrian Kurds to enjoy citizenship rights |author= |url=http://english.ruvr.ru/2011/04/06/48519940.html |newspaper= |date=2011-04-06 |accessdate=2011-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110407151355/http://english.ruvr.ru/2011/04/06/48519940.html |archive-date=2011-04-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

;4月8日-“'''反抗星期五'''”
[[File:Syrian_Demonstration_Douma_Damascus_08-04-2011.jpg|thumb]]的Douma地区举行的反政府示威活动]]
作为第三个星期五，示威活动的口号为“反抗星期五”（Friday of Resistance），数千名抗议者走上[[德拉|德拉]]、[[拉塔基亚|拉塔基亚]]、[[塔尔图斯|塔尔图斯]]、[[Edlib|Edlib]]、[[巴尼亚斯|巴尼亚斯]]、[[卡米什利|卡米什利]]、[[霍姆斯|霍姆斯]]和[[大马士革|大马士革]]的郊区[[Harasta|Harasta]]进行示威<ref>{{Cite web |author=Katherine Marsh in Damascus |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/apr/08/syria-unrest-killed-damascus-assad |title=Syria's biggest day of unrest yet sees at least 20 people killed |work=The Guardian |location=UK |date= |accessdate=2011-04-10 |archive-date=2011-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110411181350/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/apr/08/syria-unrest-killed-damascus-assad |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=AlJazeera090411>{{Cite news|title=Protesters killed in southern Syria|publisher=AL Jazeera|date=9 April 2011|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/201148131548860250.html|accessdate=9 April 2011|archive-date=2011-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110409035352/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/201148131548860250.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在[[德拉|德拉]]，有27名抗议者被开枪的部队所杀，更多人则是受了伤<ref name=AlJazeera090411/><ref>[http://www.france24.com/en/20110408-syrian-security-forces-shoot-dead-13-protesters Syrian security forces 'shoot dead 13 protesters'] {{Wayback|url=http://www.france24.com/en/20110408-syrian-security-forces-shoot-dead-13-protesters |date=20110513013741 }}, ''[[France_24|France 24]]'', 8 April 2011</ref>。一个活动家在电话里告诉记者说，示威的人群从三个清真寺里出来，当他们行进到该市的法院的时候，遇上了穿着平民服装的安全部队的阻拦，双方产生了冲突。<ref name="BBC Deraa">[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-13016843 Syrian city of Deraa hit by deadly clashes] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-13016843 |date=20120205023224 }}, ''BBC'', 8 April 2011</ref>抗议者向总统阿萨德的亲兄[[巴塞勒·阿萨德|巴塞勒·阿萨德]]的雕像投掷石块，并在复兴党的哨点放火<ref name="BBC Deraa"/><ref>{{Cite web |title=Syria protesters torch party outpost, smash statue |date=2011-04-08 |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/08/cb-syria-protests-statue-idUSLDE7371LA20110408 |publisher=Reuters |accessdate=2012-01-02 |archive-date=2011-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511190042/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/08/cb-syria-protests-statue-idUSLDE7371LA20110408 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。国家电视台报道说，截止目前已经有19名警察和安全部队成員在德拉被杀<ref>[http://www.sandiegouniontribune.com/sdut-syria-says-19-police-killed-in-southern-city-2011apr08-story.html Syria says 19 police killed in southern city] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sandiegouniontribune.com/sdut-syria-says-19-police-killed-in-southern-city-2011apr08-story.html |date=20161020110104 }}, 2011-04-08.</ref>。

在大马士革的郊区城'''Harasta'''，至少有三人被杀；在第三大城市[[霍姆斯|霍姆斯]]，有两人死亡，数十人受伤<ref>{{Cite web |title=Syria: government troops in violent reaction to fresh protests |date=2011-04-08 |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/8438932/Syria-government-troops-in-violent-reaction-to-fresh-protests.html |publisher=Telegraph |accessdate=2012-01-02 |archive-date=2012-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120106194226/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/8438932/Syria-government-troops-in-violent-reaction-to-fresh-protests.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一个人权组织说周五全国有37人被杀<ref name="NYTIMES" />。

;4月9日
在德拉的目击者说，有几千人在一个清真寺附近参加大葬礼，部队使用枪炮和催类瓦斯对他们进行驱赶<ref>{{Cite news|last=al-Khalidi|first=Suleiman|title=Syrian forces fire at mourners after mass funeral|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/09/syria-deraa-violence-idUSLDE7380B120110409|accessdate=9 April 2011|agency=Reuters|date=9 April 2011|location=[[Amman|Amman]]|quote=They said security forces used live ammunition and tear gas to disperse thousands of Syrians who were chanting freedom slogans, after assembling close to the mosque in the old quarter of the city near the border with Jordan.|archive-date=2011-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111224090455/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/09/syria-deraa-violence-idUSLDE7380B120110409|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在[[拉塔基亚|拉塔基亚]]，目击者说部队用枪炮驱散举行抗议的几百人。另一个目击者说有洒水车在不断进出以清除大街上的血迹<ref>{{Cite news|last=Oweis|first=Khaled Yacoub|title=Syrian forces fire at mourners after mass funeral|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/09/us-syria-idUSTRE72N2MC20110409|accessdate=9 April 2011|agency=Reuters|date=9 April 2011|location=[[Amman|Amman]]|quote=In the early hours of Saturday, Syrian security forces used live ammunition to disperse a pro-democracy protest by hundreds of people in a Sunni district of Latakia, causing scores of injuries and possible deaths, residents said.|archive-date=2011-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111220020007/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/09/us-syria-idUSTRE72N2MC20110409|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

;4月10日
据报道在9日：德拉有26人死亡；<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=260044#ixzz1J6bFhur3 |title=Syria forces killed 28 protesters, rights activists say |publisher=AFP/NOW Lebanon |date=2011-04-10 |accessdate=2011-04-10 }}{{Dead link|date=2019年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>[[霍姆斯|霍姆斯]]有20人死亡；[[巴尼亚斯|巴尼亚斯]]有1人死亡<ref name="NL110410">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=253828 |title=Syria: 10 April 2011 |publisher=AFP/NOW Lebanon |date=2011-04-10 |accessdate=2011-04-10 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120906140521/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=253828 |archivedate=2012-09-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

4月10日上午，在[[巴尼亚斯|巴尼亚斯]]的大清真寺前举行的示威活动中，军队朝人群开枪，导致至少4人死亡。在[[霍姆斯|霍姆斯]]，[[Douma|Douma]]和德拉也有示威发生<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/201141011216603387.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-02 |archive-date=2011-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110415094227/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/201141011216603387.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根据官方新闻机构（Sana）的报道，一个9名士兵组成的小队在[[巴尼亚斯|巴尼亚斯]]附近的路上被埋伏的枪手射杀，其中包括两名长官，另外还有其他许多受伤者。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sana.sy/fra/51/2011/04/10/341067.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111005094323/http://sana.sy/fra/51/2011/04/10/341067.htm |archive-date=2011-10-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>http://www.allvoices.com/contributed-news/8747229-nine-soldiers-were-killed-in-an-ambush-and-four-dead-by-security-forces-in-banias{{Dead link|date=2018年9月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} Nine soldiers were killed in an ambush and four dead by security forces in Banias</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.shukumaku.com/Content.php?id=26279 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110518183136/http://www.shukumaku.com/Content.php?id=26279 |archive-date=2011-05-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

=== 中旬 ===
;4月11日
[[大马士革大学|大马士革大学]]的科学院学生，聚集在'''Baramkeh'''地区，举行了高喊要求自由的示威活动，同时也表达他们对[[德拉|德拉]]和[[巴尼亚斯|巴尼亚斯]]发生的示威活动的支持。不过，该学院的院长Mohammad否认有此事的发生，他说有许多学生聚集在学院前面是在表达反对破坏叙利亚稳定的行为和在支持总统<ref>http://www.dp-news.com/pages/detail.aspx?l=2&articleid=80561{{Dead link|date=2020年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} DayPress news:Pressure mounted on Syria</ref><ref>http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qH1xkZ-6dgs {{Wayback|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qH1xkZ-6dgs |date=20160202052911 }} Rally in support of Mr. Bashar Al-Assad at Damascus University-Faculty of Sciences</ref>。在[[巴尼亚斯|巴尼亚斯]]，举行了一场为被军队打死的四名抗议者的葬礼活动，后来演变为新的示威抗议活动，部队则直到晚上一直在攻击他们<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/2011411143055997548.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-02 |archive-date=2011-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110415090712/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/2011411143055997548.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;4月12日
证实在11日大马士革大学学生举行的示威抗议活动中，有一个学生被部队打死。有目击者说在[[巴尼亚斯|巴尼亚斯]]'''Bayda'''的郊区，[[坦克|坦克]]和枪炮包围着正在进行的示威人群，导致几十人受伤<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-13046990|title=Syria: 'Dozens injured' in Baniyas as arrests continue|publisher=BBC|accessdate=12-04-2010|archive-date=2011-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110518021101/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-13046990|dead-url=no}}</ref>，救护车和来自[[塔尔图斯|塔尔图斯]]援助的食物都被禁止进入该村。

;4月13日
数百名妇女参加了一个游行，她们要求释放在Bayda镇被逮捕的350个男人。在[[阿勒颇大学|阿勒颇大学]]的文学院发生的抗议活动，学生与部队发生了冲突，三名学生被逮捕。在大马士革，大约50个学生在法学院举行了一个要求自由的抗议活动<ref name="AJ13AprSyria">{{cite news |title=Syrian protests spread to Aleppo |author= |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/201141315543918716.html |newspaper= |date=13 April 2011 |accessdate=13 April 2011 |archive-date=2011-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110416210628/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/201141315543918716.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;4月14日
阿萨德总统宣布释放几百名“没有参与暴力活动”的囚犯，并且宣告新政府已经成立了。阿萨德会见一个来自德拉的示威者代表团，这是他首次与示威者们进行直接接触<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-13084656 Syria: President Assad forms new government] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-13084656 |date=20171011193529 }}, ''[[BBC_News|BBC News]]'', 14 April 2011</ref><ref>[http://www.thenational.ae/news/worldwide/syria-president-appoints-new-government-orders-protesters-freed-from-jail Syria president appoints new government, orders protesters freed from jail] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thenational.ae/news/worldwide/syria-president-appoints-new-government-orders-protesters-freed-from-jail |date=20111227115827 }}, Phil Sands, ''The National'', 15 April 2011</ref>。

在[[苏韦达|苏韦达]]有300人举行抗议活动<ref>{{cite news|title=Protest erupts in Syria's Druze heartland: witness|author=Reporting by Khaled Yacoub Oweis; editing by Janet Lawrence|newspaper=Reuters|date=2011-04-14|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/14/us-syria-protests-druze-idUSTRE73D6UN20110414|accessdate=2011-04-15|archive-date=2011-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110418062126/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/14/us-syria-protests-druze-idUSTRE73D6UN20110414|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

;4月15日-“'''决心星期五'''”
当天的口号是“决心星期五”（Friday of determination），在巴尼亚斯、拉塔基亚、Baida、霍姆斯和[[代爾祖爾|代爾祖爾]]这几个城市有共计数万人参加了抗议<ref>{{cite news|title=Thousands demand Syria reforms|author=Press Association|date=15 Apr 2011|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ukpress/article/ALeqM5jN76aN1xO-jx1SDSM2d3TOIFa8vw?docId=N0611591302874520983A|accessdate=15 Apr 2011}}</ref><ref name="AJ15AprilSyria"/>。半島报道说，有多达5万名抗议者努力从Douma进入大马士革，他们被使用催泪瓦斯的安全部队驱散；而在大马士革的Barzeh地区，当大量部队包围着聚集在清真寺前面的250人的抗议人群时，发生了暴力事件<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/live/middle-east/live-blog-middle-east-protests-april-15 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-02 |archive-date=2011-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110415103341/http://blogs.aljazeera.net/live/middle-east/live-blog-middle-east-protests-april-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另一边，在德拉有数千人举行了抗议活动，由于有报道说政府允许示威活动所以部队并没有出现。<ref name="AJ15AprilSyria">{{cite news |title=Thousands take to streets in Syria protests |author=[[Al-Jazeera_English|Al-Jazeera English]] |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/201141511585431229.html |newspaper= |date=15 April 2011 |accessdate=15 April 2011 |archive-date=2011-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110416111258/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/201141511585431229.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

;4月16日
在德拉，有数千人举行了高喊反政府口号的示威；在大马士革郊区Douma，1500个居民举行静坐，他们要求释放在前些天被逮捕的140人。<ref name="Reuters16AprSyria">{{cite news |title=Syria's Assad vows to lift emergency law by next week |author= |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/16/us-syria-idUSTRE72N2MC20110416 |newspaper= |date=16 April 2011 |accessdate=17 April 2011 |archive-date=2011-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110906021220/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/16/us-syria-idUSTRE72N2MC20110416 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

在以色列控制的戈兰高地的'''Majdal Shams'''地区，大约200人举行了反叙利亚政府的示威<ref>{{cite news|title=200 Druze rally against Assad in Majdal Shams|author=Hagai Einav|newspaper=Ynetnews|date=16 April 2011|url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/1,7340,L-4057595,00.html|accessdate=23 April 2011|archive-date=2012-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025042121/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/1,7340,L-4057595,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4057638,00.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-02 |archive-date=2012-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120110052248/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4057638,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

4月16日，敘利亞总统發表电视讲话，表示将会废除紧急状态法；他承认政府与国民之间存在裂口，政府不得不“要跟上人民的愿望”，他的内阁稍后会作出更详细的说明<ref name="Syria to lift emergency law">{{cite news |title=Syria to lift emergency law |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/20114161511286268.html |date=2011-04-16 |accessdate=2011-04-17 |archive-date=2011-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110417110609/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/20114161511286268.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>（[http://www.dp-news.com/pages/detail.aspx?l=2&articleid=81032 全文]{{Dead link|date=2020年6月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}）；他也说“政府和国民团结一致”的重要性；强调采取对话解决问题，公众对政府的支持和信任等是急需的；解释说改革与公民的需求，安全与尊严是相互关联的。他说解决库尔德人的公民权是优先要走的一步，之后政党法、地方组织和选举法，以及新的现代媒体法等一系列改革都被列入了时间表内。接下来还要解决失业、经济、农村服务、吸引投资、公私领域、正义、腐败和受贿行为，税法改革和减少政府浪费等各种问题，这都需要更多公民和组织的参与，以使它们解决地更有效率。

;4月17日
在[[苏韦达|苏韦达]]，大约300人举行示威，但被安全部队驱散。报道说，在阿勒颇、巴尼亚斯、霍姆斯和Hirak也有示威活动，他们大部分都高喊了要求政治自由的口号。叙利亚国家新闻机构[[SANA|SANA]]报道说，隐藏在卡车上来自于伊拉克的大量武器已被扣押<ref>{{cite news |title=Syrians protest despite Assad concessions |author= |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/2011417131422534165.html |newspaper= |date=17 April 2011 |accessdate=17 April 2011 |archive-date=2011-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110420130818/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/04/2011417131422534165.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在Talbiseh镇的一个公路上，安全部队朝正在举行的葬礼人群开火，打死三人。在霍姆斯，由于一个部落领袖在监禁中死亡，抗议者与部队产生了冲突，导致12名抗议者被杀<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/international/syria-city-boiling-after-security-forces-reportedly-kill-12-protesters-1.356647 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-02 |archive-date=2011-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110419220738/http://www.haaretz.com/news/international/syria-city-boiling-after-security-forces-reportedly-kill-12-protesters-1.356647 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;4月18日
